{"tid":2421252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"預算案撥 80 億未來數年「維護國安」 已達新疆一年維穩費三分一","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T04:07:45.000Z","uid":44209,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"840ec5e4418e1bf18d396d14b8339f392a81ed20","tid":2421252,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"【預算案撥 80 億未來數年「維護國安」 已達新疆一年維穩費三分一】<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波今天（24 日）發表財政預算案，增撥 80 億用於支付關於「維護國家安全」未來數年的開支，是港府首度將「維護國家安全」開支納入預算當中；根據《港區國安法》條文，政府要從一般收入中撥款，支付關於維護國家安全的開支，並不受本港現行法律規定限制。<br />\n<br />\n80 億有幾多？根據《中國統計年鑑 2020》，中國各地之中，2019 年人均公共安全開支頭四名分別是西藏、北京、新疆、上海。雖然中國官方預算並沒有「維穩」開支的說法，但外界一直認為最接近說法，正是這筆「公共安全支出」。<br />\n<br />\n今日預算案撥出 80 億未來數年「維護國安」，以香港人口 740 萬人計，即每人平均付出 1,070 元。香港這片彈丸之地的「維穩費」，已達新疆一年的三分一。<br />\n<br />\n另見報道：<br />\n首設 80 億「維護國家安全」開支 涉「未來數年」開支 編制部門不明<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aQ7scR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aQ7scR&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=9887ff8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aQ7scR</a><br />\n<br />\n撥 80 億「維護國安」 陳茂波稱「機密資料」拒交代細節<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MktISx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MktISx&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=1a0d1990\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MktISx</a><br />\n<br />\n財政預算案報道一覽：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/tag/2021財政預算案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftag%2F2021%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=de08874f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ftag%2F2021%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88&h=0cbd078b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/tag/2021財政預算案</a>"},{"pid":"34701c4fbab812dea715c5281e025ac6b1c7f68b","tid":2421252,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"【香港首度開設國安維穩費 失業高企之際強搶80億養國安】<br />\n<br />\n在香港失業率突破7%，創16年新高，經濟比去年萎縮 6.1%，成為有紀錄以來最差的一年時，香港政府不但拒絕派錢、只肯分期付款派消費券，是有紀錄還要首次強徵納稅人80億養國安監控香港人，還有加257億資源給黑警， 明正言順殘民自肥。<br />\n<br />\n當國安維穩費差不多是三萬黑警撥款的一半時，大家估下中共駐港國安特務規模有多大？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkfp/status/1364478735257395208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkfp%2Fstatus%2F1364478735257395208&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=8714182f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkfp%2Fstatus%2F1364478735257395208&h=94e966a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkfp/status/1364478735257395208</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tomgrundy/status/1364480081234563073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftomgrundy%2Fstatus%2F1364480081234563073&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=a4b4520e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftomgrundy%2Fstatus%2F1364480081234563073&h=b542f82b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tomgrundy/status/1364480081234563073</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1364447327105130501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FXinqiSu%2Fstatus%2F1364447327105130501&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=d31041fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FXinqiSu%2Fstatus%2F1364447327105130501&h=2802ac46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1364447327105130501</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/galileocheng/status/1364454291730178054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgalileocheng%2Fstatus%2F1364454291730178054&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=318a1688\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgalileocheng%2Fstatus%2F1364454291730178054&h=fbdb0e96\" data-auto-link t