Z","msg":"所謂嘅用錢維護国家安全，唔係派錢塞住你把口，係不斷用錢去上訴同上訴，同埋買新裝備去打鳩你"},{"pid":"ea2b7e65e83b67cd0f9b274c441aff935a9853c6","tid":2421252,"uid":203889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"抽水俾大陸姐<br />\n遲早抽乾"},{"pid":"8146ea45db07287ed46817e007cab361c5e74ad1","tid":2421252,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"進貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a6ce6c3fa6c0ea8cd9bfb6f7598e282c6265bc","tid":2421252,"uid":261937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"交80億保護費咁貴! 邊班陀地?"},{"pid":"d89a54bbce2bdd6aa24238d298bc5a8115b964ae","tid":2421252,"uid":114781,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"新疆人口： 2600萬<br />\n香港人口：750萬<br />\n以人口計香港維穩費最高，仲未計狗隊大幅增加嘅預算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港已離新疆不遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c32aa6bdbec1d3368bec5788d8d09343739ad6f","tid":2421252,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d89a54bbce2bdd6aa24238d298bc5a8115b964ae","tid":2421252,"uid":114781,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"新疆人口： 2600萬<br />\n香港人口：750萬<br />\n以人口計香港維穩費最高，仲未計狗隊大幅增加嘅預算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港已離新疆不遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:41:18.000Z","msg":"推呢個啦"},{"pid":"541914af710356ec95e3164cb4bf7c18e01bfd09","tid":2421252,"uid":8745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"國安油水fat fat"},{"pid":"1822fc63168b89d4ff38224cd20160f17dcc988b","tid":2421252,"uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:59:03.000Z","msg":"其實大陸既維穩費, 係包括埋 國安, 公安, 海關, 法院, 監獄 等等所有執法部門既運作開支<br />\n<br />\n而香港呢80億就專門負責國安.........警察, 海關 法院 ,懲教 既開支另外再計<br />\n<br />\n所以咁計法, 香港既國安開支 係高過大陸維穩費"},{"pid":"13f3e6a271b34c5514952c3566440c77fc2277d1","tid":2421252,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"就嚟可以同NSA有得揮"},{"pid":"4ac904c8780a56133cfa61922a5feaddce80be53","tid":2421252,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:12:46.000Z","msg":"而家出嚟做戲嗰班都係黑警國安處，支那嗰班淨係大粒嘢浦過頭，下面細嗰啲有幾多人完全唔知，不過經過維景都見過啲支那平頭裝喺度煲煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0b16a55e744e2f75adec9e77eebb27d6103b8f","tid":2421252,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"你以為真心幫你維護國家安全？<br />\n撈油水咋"},{"pid":"94d41e3a9ae758e74c8c121e0617a34403bb0d60","tid":2421252,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:16:01.000Z","msg":"其實可以用成萬億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗大嶼咁煩"},{"pid":"45c8dc3561b0d329c4f91261bd018efe8eee6a11","tid":2421252,"uid":294356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:16:22.000Z","msg":"80億可以起幾多個毒氣室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8695919538ace27413332eb99f8fff08c642e6","tid":2421252,"uid":103146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a6ce6c3fa6c0ea8cd9bfb6f7598e282c6265bc","tid":2421252,"uid":261937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"交80億保護費咁貴! 邊班陀地?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"全球最大黑社會：中国共產黨<br />\n<br />\n製毒走私起家個個都知"},{"pid":"152f75a9e2adfb1ad984f2972f7f42fa8cc5a5f2","tid":2421252,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"比美國制裁果班D樓咪就係用呢筆錢找數囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"